---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = '23 April 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | Beyond Border Group"
  description="How Beyond Border Group collects, uses and protects personal information. Privacy practices for our website and services."
>
  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1 class="legal-hero__title">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal-hero__meta">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
      <p class="legal-hero__lead">
        Beyond Border Group is operated by BeyondBorderGroup LTD, a Hong Kong SAR registered
        entity. We respect the privacy of every visitor and client. This policy explains what
        personal data we collect, how we use it, how we store it, and who we share it with when
        you visit our website or engage our services.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section legal-body">
    <div class="container">
      <article class="prose">
        <h2>Information we collect</h2>

        <h3>Personal data</h3>
        <p>
          We collect the information you voluntarily provide to us: your name, email address,
          company name, phone number, and any other details you share through our contact form,
          by email, or in the course of a service engagement.
        </p>

        <h3>Non-personal data</h3>
        <p>
          When you visit our website, we automatically collect technical information such as your
          IP address, browser type, operating system, referring URL, pages viewed, and session
          duration. This is gathered through cookies and similar technologies. See our
          <a href="/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a> for details.
        </p>

        <h2>How we use your information</h2>

        <h3>Personal information</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>To respond to your inquiries and requests</li>
          <li>To deliver the services you have asked us to provide</li>
          <li>To send marketing communications, where you have given consent</li>
          <li>To process transactions and manage client accounts</li>
          <li>To improve and extend our service offerings</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Non-personal information</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>To analyse website traffic and performance</li>
          <li>To improve the user experience on the site</li>
          <li>To generate aggregated, anonymised statistical reports</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Information sharing</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell, trade or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share
          your data with trusted service providers who help us operate our website and deliver
          our services, and who are bound by confidentiality obligations. We may also disclose
          personal information when required by law, or where we believe disclosure is necessary
          to protect our rights, our clients, or the public.
        </p>

        <h2>Data protection and retention</h2>
        <p>
          We apply technical and organisational safeguards designed to protect personal data
          against unauthorised access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. We keep personal
          data for only as long as is necessary for the purposes for which it was collected, or
          as required by applicable law.
        </p>

        <h2>Your rights</h2>
        <p>
          You have the right to access the personal data we hold about you, request corrections,
          ask us to delete it, object to how we process it, and withdraw any consent you have
          previously given. To exercise any of these rights, contact us using the details below.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-party links</h2>
        <p>
          Our website may contain links to external websites. We are not responsible for the
          privacy practices or content of any third-party site. We encourage you to read the
          privacy policy of every site you visit.
        </p>

        <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our services are not directed at individuals under 18. We do not knowingly collect
          personal data from children. If we become aware that a child has provided us with
          personal data, we will delete it promptly.
        </p>

        <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The revised version will be
          posted on this page with an updated date. We encourage you to review this page
          periodically.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or about how we handle your personal
          data, email <a href="mailto:hello@beyondbordergroup.com">hello@beyondbordergroup.com</a>
          or use our <a href="/contact">contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-hero {
    background: var(--bbg-surface);
    padding: var(--space-7) 0 var(--space-6);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--bbg-border);
  }
  .legal-hero .container > * { max-width: 760px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .legal-hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4vw + 1rem, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--bbg-ink);
    margin: var(--space-3) auto var(--space-3);
  }
  .legal-hero__meta {
    font-size: var(--fs-small);
    color: var(--bbg-text-muted);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-5);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .legal-hero__lead {
    font-size: var(--fs-lead);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--bbg-text);
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .legal-body { padding-top: var(--space-7); padding-bottom: var(--space-7); }

  .prose {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--bbg-text);
    font-size: var(--fs-body);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .prose h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--bbg-ink);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin: var(--space-7) 0 var(--space-3);
    line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .prose h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .prose h3 {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--bbg-ink);
    margin: var(--space-5) 0 var(--space-2);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }
  .prose p { margin: 0 0 var(--space-4); }
  .prose ul {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-4);
  }
  .prose li { margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
  .prose a { color: var(--bbg-blue); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
  .prose a:hover { color: var(--bbg-blue-dark); }
</style>
